      "content": "the thing is, i just heard from the warehouse that the big shipment is delayed by like a month. so we're definitely gonna run out. won't it look bad if we keep them listed and then have to cancel everyone's orders halfway through the week? i'm starting to think we should just pull them from the site for now.",
